---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Social Media Management — Federica Fanì"
  description="Gestione profili social, contenuti, fotografia e analytics per brand e locali. Autenticità prima di tutto."
>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="smm-hero">
    <div class="smm-hero-inner">
      <div class="breadcrumb reveal">
        <a href="/servizi">Servizi</a>
        <span>→</span>
        <span>Social Media Management</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Social Media<br><em>Management</em></h1>
      <p class="smm-hero-sub reveal reveal-delay-2">
        I social sono pieni di contenuti. Quello che manca, quasi sempre, è la personalità.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- APPROCCIO -->
  <section class="section approach-section">
    <div class="approach-grid">
      <div class="approach-text">
        <span class="eyebrow reveal">Il mio approccio</span>
        <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Autenticità prima di tutto</h2>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2">Parto sempre da una domanda semplice: cosa rende unico questo posto, questo brand, questa persona? Poi costruiamo tutto il resto attorno a quella risposta: strategia, contenuti, foto, video. Perché un profilo che converte è prima di tutto un profilo che sembra vero.</p>
        <div class="approach-list reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <div class="approach-item">
            <span class="approach-check">✓</span>
            <span>Gestione completa del profilo (Instagram, Facebook, TikTok)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="approach-item">
            <span class="approach-check">✓</span>
            <span>Creazione contenuti: caption, grafica, Reels, Stories</span>
          </div>
          <div class="approach-item">
            <span class="approach-check">✓</span>
            <span>Fotografia e riprese in loco (Pigneto e zona Roma Est)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="approach-item">
            <span class="approach-check">✓</span>
            <span>Pianificazione editoriale e calendario contenuti</span>
          </div>
          <div class="approach-item">
            <span class="approach-check">✓</span>
            <span>Monitoraggio e analisi delle performance mensili</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="approach-side reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="approach-stat">
          <div class="stat-big">3+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Anni di esperienza</div>
        </div>
        <div class="approach-stat">
          <div class="stat-big">IT · EN · ES</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Contenuti multilingue</div>
        </div>
        <div class="approach-stat">
          <div class="stat-big">Roma</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Foto in loco (zona Pigneto)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PREZZI -->
  <div class="section-dark">
    <section class="section pricing-section">
      <div class="sec-header">
        <div class="sec-header-left">
          <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-light reveal">Investimento</span>
          <h2 class="sec-title-light reveal reveal-delay-1">Pacchetti SMM</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="pricing-sub reveal reveal-delay-2">Tutti i pacchetti includono report mensile delle performance. Preventivo personalizzato su richiesta.</p>

      <div class="pricing-grid">

        <div class="pricing-card reveal">
          <div class="pricing-label">Starter</div>
          <div class="pricing-price">
            <span class="p-val">€400</span>
            <span class="p-period">/mese</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pricing-desc">Ideale per chi inizia o vuole testare la gestione social professionale.</div>
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>1 piattaforma (Instagram o Facebook)</li>
            <li>8–10 post al mese</li>
            <li>Caption e grafica incluse</li>
            <li>Piano editoriale mensile</li>
            <li>Report performance base</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="pricing-note">Foto in loco non incluse (pacchetto separato)</div>
          <a href="/contatti" class="btn btn-outline-light pricing-btn">Richiedi info</a>
        </div>

        <div class="pricing-card pricing-card-featured reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="pricing-label-featured">Più scelto</div>
          <div class="pricing-label">Standard</div>
          <div class="pricing-price">
            <span class="p-val">€700</span>
            <span class="p-period">/mese</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pricing-desc">Gestione completa con fotografia in loco. Il pacchetto più richiesto per locali e attività commerciali.</div>
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>2 piattaforme (Instagram + Facebook)</li>
            <li>12–15 post al mese</li>
            <li>Stories e Reels inclusi</li>
            <li>1 sessione foto in loco al mese</li>
            <li>Piano editoriale mensile</li>
            <li>Report performance completo</li>
            <li>Gestione commenti e DM</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contatti" class="btn btn-gold pricing-btn">Richiedi preventivo</a>
        </div>

        <div class="pricing-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="pricing-label">Premium</div>
          <div class="pricing-price">
            <span class="p-val">€1.200</span>
            <span class="p-period">/mese</span>
          </div>
          <div class="pricing-desc">Gestione multi-canale completa con analytics avanzate. Per brand che vogliono crescere in modo strutturato.</div>
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>3 piattaforme (Instagram + Facebook + TikTok)</li>
            <li>20+ contenuti al mese</li>
            <li>Reels, Stories, TikTok video</li>
            <li>2 sessioni foto in loco al mese</li>
            <li>Strategia editoriale trimestrale</li>
            <li>Analytics avanzate con Looker Studio</li>
            <li>Gestione completa commenti e DM</li>
            <li>Consulenza mensile 1:1</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contatti" class="btn btn-outline-light pricing-btn">Richiedi info</a>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="pricing-extra reveal">
        <div class="extra-title">Servizi aggiuntivi</div>
        <div class="extra-grid">
          <div class="extra-item">
            <span class="extra-name">Sessione fotografica extra</span>
            <span class="extra-price">da €150</span>
          </div>
          <div class="extra-item">
            <span class="extra-name">Setup profilo da zero</span>
            <span class="extra-price">€200 una tantum</span>
          </div>
          <div class="extra-item">
            <span class="extra-name">Gestione Meta Ads (paid)</span>
            <span class="extra-price">€150/mese + budget ads</span>
          </div>
          <div class="extra-item">
            <span class="extra-name">Contenuti multilingue (EN/ES)</span>
            <span class="extra-price">+€100/mese</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pricing-disclaimer reveal">
        Tutti i prezzi sono IVA esclusa. I pacchetti hanno durata minima di 3 mesi. Preventivo personalizzato disponibile per esigenze specifiche.
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- PER CHI -->
  <section class="section forchi-section">
    <div class="sec-header">
      <div class="sec-header-left">
        <span class="eyebrow reveal">Per chi</span>
        <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Lavoro bene con</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="forchi-grid">
      <div class="forchi-item reveal">
        <div class="forchi-ico">🍸</div>
        <div class="forchi-title">Bar e locali</div>
        <div class="forchi-desc">Dalla gestione social al calendario eventi, fotografia in loco inclusa. Magnebevo è il mio cliente principale da oltre un anno.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="forchi-item reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="forchi-ico">🛍️</div>
        <div class="forchi-title">Negozi e attività commerciali</div>
        <div class="forchi-desc">Prodotti, promozioni, storytelling del brand. Contenuti che vendono senza sembrare pubblicità.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="forchi-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="forchi-ico">👤</div>
        <div class="forchi-title">Professionisti e freelance</div>
        <div class="forchi-desc">Personal branding, posizionamento, visibilità online. Da remoto, per qualsiasi settore.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="forchi-item reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="forchi-ico">🌍</div>
        <div class="forchi-title">Brand internazionali</div>
        <div class="forchi-desc">Contenuti in italiano, inglese, spagnolo e francese. Senza affidarsi a traduttori esterni.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="section-dark">
    <section class="section cta-section">
      <div class="cta-inner">
        <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-light reveal">Parliamo</span>
        <h2 class="sec-title-light reveal reveal-delay-1">Iniziamo?</h2>
        <p class="cta-sub reveal reveal-delay-2">Scrivimi per un preventivo personalizzato o per capire insieme quale pacchetto fa al caso tuo.</p>
        <div class="cta-btns reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <a href="/contatti" class="btn btn-gold">Scrivimi</a>
          <a href="/servizi" class="btn btn-outline-light">Tutti i servizi</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

</Layout>

<style>
/* HERO */
.smm-hero {
  padding: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px) clamp(20px, 5vw, 80px) clamp(32px, 4vw, 56px);
  background: var(--blue-pale);
}

.smm-hero-inner { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }

.breadcrumb {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--blue-mid);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.breadcrumb a { color: var(--blue); transition: opacity 0.2s; }
.breadcrumb a:hover { opacity: 0.7; }

.smm-hero h1 {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 72px);
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--blue-dark);
  line-height: 1.1;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.smm-hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--blue); }

.smm-hero-sub {
  font-size: 16px;
  color: var(--blue-mid);
  font-style: italic;
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
}

/* APPROACH */
.approach-section { padding-top: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px); padding-bottom: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px); }

.approach-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
  gap: clamp(40px, 6vw, 80px);
  align-items: start;
}

.approach-text h2 { color: var(--blue-dark); margin-bottom: 16px; }
.approach-text p { font-size: 15px; color: var(--blue-mid); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 24px; }

.approach-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }

.approach-item {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 12px;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--blue-mid);
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.approach-check {
  color: var(--blue);
  font-weight: 500;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 1px;
}

.approach-side {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 20px;
}

.approach-stat {
  padding: 20px;
  background: var(--blue-light);
  border-radius: var(--r-md);
  border: 0.5px solid rgba(43,79,216,0.15);
}

.stat-big {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 28px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--blue);
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}

.stat-label { font-size: 11px; color: var(--blue-mid); letter-spacing: 0.06em; }

/* PRICING */
.pricing-section { padding-top: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px); padding-bottom: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px); }

.pricing-sub {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--azure);
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  font-style: italic;
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
}

.pricing-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}

.pricing-card {
  background: rgba(43,79,216,0.1);
  border: 0.5px solid rgba(123,167,232,0.2);
  border-radius: var(--r-lg);
  padding: 28px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 16px;
  position: relative;
}

.pricing-card-featured {
  background: rgba(43,79,216,0.2);
  border-color: rgba(123,167,232,0.5);
}

.pricing-label-featured {
  position: absolute;
  top: -12px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  background: var(--gold);
  color: var(--gold-dark);
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  padding: 4px 14px;
  border-radius: 20px;
  white-space: nowrap;
}

.pricing-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--azure);
}

.pricing-price {
  display: flex;
  align-items: baseline;
  gap: 4px;
}

.p-val {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 42px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--white);
  line-height: 1;
}

.p-period { font-size: 14px; color: var(--azure); }

.pricing-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--azure); line-height: 1.6; }

.pricing-features {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 8px;
  flex: 1;
}

.pricing-features li {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: rgba(123,167,232,0.9);
  padding-left: 16px;
  position: relative;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.pricing-features li::before {
  content: '→';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0;
  color: var(--blue);
  font-size: 12px;
}

.pricing-note {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: rgba(123,167,232,0.5);
  font-style: italic;
}

.pricing-btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; margin-top: auto; }

/* EXTRA */
.pricing-extra {
  background: rgba(43,79,216,0.08);
  border: 0.5px solid rgba(123,167,232,0.15);
  border-radius: var(--r-lg);
  padding: 24px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.extra-title {
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--azure);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.extra-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 10px;
}

.extra-item {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  background: rgba(43,79,216,0.1);
  border-radius: var(--r-sm);
  gap: 12px;
}

.extra-name { font-size: 13px; color: var(--azure); }
.extra-price { font-size: 13px; color: var(--white); font-weight: 500; white-space: nowrap; }

.pricing-disclaimer {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: rgba(123,167,232,0.4);
  text-align: center;
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* FOR WHO */
.forchi-section { padding-top: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px); padding-bottom: clamp(48px, 6vw, 80px); }

.forchi-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 16px;
}

.forchi-item {
  background: var(--white);
  border: 0.5px solid rgba(43,79,216,0.12);
  border-radius: var(--r-lg);
  padding: 24px;
  transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
}

.forchi-item:hover {
  transform: translateY(-3px);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(43,79,216,0.08);
}

.forchi-ico { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.forchi-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--blue-dark); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.forchi-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--blue-mid); line-height: 1.7; }

/* CTA */
.cta-section { text-align: center; }
.cta-section .eyebrow { display: block; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.cta-section h2 { margin-bottom: 16px; }
.cta-sub { font-size: 15px; color: var(--azure); max-width: 480px; margin: 0 auto 32px; line-height: 1.75; }
.cta-btns { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

/* RESPONSIVE */
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .pricing-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 480px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  .forchi-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .approach-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .approach-side { flex-direction: row; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .approach-stat { flex: 1; min-width: 140px; }
  .extra-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .forchi-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
